Description
-----------

The mask\_right keywork only allows sound from the shader to be outbut
through the right surround sound speaker in a 5.1 setup or the right
speaker in a 2 channel (stereo) setup.

Usage
-----

    mask_right

Example
-------

    ship_engine_rumble
    {
        mindistance 100
        maxdistance 1000
        volume 10
        looping
        mask_backleft
        shakes .1
        sound/last_stand/loop_rumble_right_b.wav
    }
